OL,3,CGuernsey States proposes to increase
OL,4,Cthe minimum wage
OL,6,Fis inviting islanders to comment on
OL,7,Fnew plans to increase the Adult
OL,8,FMinimum Wage Rate.
OL,10,FNew proposals released today (19
OL,11,FFebruary) propose that the should
OL,12,Fincrease from 60% of average earnings
OL,13,Fto 66% by 2030.
OL,15,FThe current rate sits at #10.65 per
OL,16,Fhour.
OL,18,FThe Committee for Employment and
OL,19,FSocial Security hopes this figure will
OL,20,Fbring into line with and the UK.
